Symbol.Script_3D:
IF gs_shadow=0 THEN SHADOW OFF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
resol gs_resol * (gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2) + 8 * (gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1) PEN gs_cont_pen
add a/2, b, 0 rotx 90
!!! Front Panel add 0, frontpanelCutYpos-rackOffset, b-frontPanelThk for ra=1 to 4 material box_mat prism_ 4, rackThk/2, -rackWidth/2, 0, 15, rackWidth/2, 0, 15, rackWidth/2, -rackHeight, 15, -rackWidth/2, -rackHeight, 15 if ra=1 then addz rackThk/2 prism_ 4, rackThk/2, -rackWidth/2+rackOffset, -rackOffset, 15, rackWidth/2-rackOffset, -rackOffset, 15, rackWidth/2-rackOffset, -rackHeight/2, 15, -rackWidth/2+rackOffset, -rackHeight/2, 15 prism_ 4, rackThk/2, rackWidth/2-rackOffset-0.02, -rackHeight+rackOffset+0.005, 15, rackWidth/2-rackOffset, -rackHeight+rackOffset+0.005, 15, rackWidth/2-rackOffset, -rackHeight+rackOffset, 15, rackWidth/2-rackOffset-0.02, -rackHeight+rackOffset, 15 del 1 endif if ra=3 then addz rackThk/2 prism_ 4, rackThk/2, -rackWidth/2+rackOffset+0.02, -rackOffset*2, 15, rackWidth/2-rackOffset-0.02, -rackOffset*2, 15, rackWidth/2-rackOffset-0.02, -rackHeight+rackOffset*2, 15, -rackWidth/2+rackOffset+0.02, -rackHeight+rackOffset*2, 15 del 1 endif
addy -rackHeight-rackOffset next ra del 4 del 1
rotx 90 resol 512 * (gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2) + 32 * (gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1) cutpolya 6, 1, 0, 0, -rad+b, 979, -a/2-frontPanelOffset, b-curvedCutDepth, 79, 0, b, 3079, a/2+frontPanelOffset, b-curvedCutDepth, 3079, a/2+frontPanelOffset, b*2, 15, -a/2-frontPanelOffset, b*2, 15 del 1 resol gs_resol * (gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2) + 8 * (gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1)
add 0, frontpanelCutYpos-frontpanelCutH-(zzyzx-frontpanelCutYpos+frontPanelOffset), b-frontPanelThk material mat2 prism_ 4, frontPanelThk, -a/2-frontPanelOffset, 0, 15, a/2+frontPanelOffset, 0, 15, a/2+frontPanelOffset, -rackHeight, 15, -a/2-frontPanelOffset, -rackHeight, 15 del 1
addy frontpanelCutYpos cutpolya 4, 1, 0, -frontpanelCutW/2, 0, 15, frontpanelCutW/2, 0, 15, frontpanelCutW/2, -frontpanelCutH, 15, -frontpanelCutW/2, -frontpanelCutH, 15 del 1 addy frontpanelCutYpos-frontpanelCutH-(zzyzx-frontpanelCutYpos+frontPanelOffset) cutpolya 4, 1, 0, -frontpanelCutW, 0, 15, frontpanelCutW, 0, 15, frontpanelCutW, -rackHeight, 15, -frontpanelCutW, -rackHeight, 15 del 1
add -a/2-frontPanelOffset+frontPanelRad/2+cutSliceWidth/2, 0, b-cutSliceDepth for slc=1 to cutSliceNum cutform 4, 1, 1+16, 0, 0, -1, 0, -cutSliceWidth/2, frontPanelRad/2, 1+2+4+8+16, cutSliceWidth/2, frontPanelRad/2, 1+2+4+8+16, cutSliceWidth/2, frontpanelCutYpos-frontpanelCutH-(zzyzx-frontpanelCutYpos+frontPanelOffset)-rackHeight, 1+2+4+8+16, -cutSliceWidth/2, frontpanelCutYpos-frontpanelCutH-(zzyzx-frontpanelCutYpos+frontPanelOffset)-rackHeight, 1+2+4+8+16 addx cutSliceWidth+cutSliceDist next slc del cutSliceNum del 1
addz b-frontPanelThk material box_mat prism_ 12, frontPanelThk, -a/2-frontPanelOffset, frontPanelRad, 79, 0, -1, 800, -a/2-frontPanelOffset+frontPanelRad, 0, 1079, a/2+frontPanelOffset-frontPanelRad, 0, 79, 1, 0, 800, a/2+frontPanelOffset, frontPanelRad, 1079, a/2+frontPanelOffset, zzyzx+frontPanelOffset-frontPanelRad, 79, 0, 1, 800, a/2+frontPanelOffset-frontPanelRad, zzyzx+frontPanelOffset, 1079, -a/2-frontPanelOffset+frontPanelRad, zzyzx+frontPanelOffset, 79, -1, 0, 800, -a/2-frontPanelOffset, zzyzx+frontPanelOffset-frontPanelRad, 1079 del 1
for slc=1 to cutSliceNum cutend next slc
cutend cutend
cutend
!!! End Of Front Panel
!!! Body material box_mat prism_ 12, b-frontPanelThk, -a/2, bodyRad, 79, 0, -1, 800, -a/2+bodyRad, 0, 1079, a/2-bodyRad, 0, 79, 1, 0, 800, a/2, bodyRad, 1079, a/2, zzyzx-bodyRad, 79, 0, 1, 800, a/2-bodyRad, zzyzx, 1079, -a/2+bodyRad, zzyzx, 79, -1, 0, 800, -a/2, zzyzx-bodyRad, 1079 !!! End Of Body
del 2
end
Symbol.Script_2D:
pen gs_cont_pen
add2 a/2, b
hotspot2 0, 0 hotspot2 0, -b hotspot2 a/2, 0 hotspot2 -a/2, 0 hotspot2 a/2+frontPanelOffset, -b+curvedCutDepth hotspot2 -a/2-frontPanelOffset, -b+curvedCutDepth hotspot2 0, -b/2
add2 0, -b
!!! *** Background Fill fill gs_fill_type POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -a/2, frontPanelThk, 1, a/2, frontPanelThk, 1, a/2, b, 1, -a/2, b, 1
POLY2_B 6, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, rad, 901, -a/2-frontPanelOffset, curvedCutDepth, 1, 0, 0, 3001, a/2+frontPanelOffset, curvedCutDepth, 3001, a/2+frontPanelOffset, frontPanelThk, 1, -a/2-frontPanelOffset, frontPanelThk, 1
del 1 del 1
Symbol.Script_1D:
eps = 0.0001
bodyRad = 0.01
frontPanelRad = 0.01 frontPanelThk = 0.02 frontPanelOffset = 0.01
rackHeight = 0.042 rackWidth = 0.145 rackOffset = 0.003 rackThk = 0.004
frontpanelCutW = rackWidth+rackOffset*2 frontpanelCutH = rackHeight*4+rackOffset*5 frontpanelCutYpos = zzyzx-0.025
!! Front Panel Cutting Slices
cutSliceWidth = 0.004 cutSliceDepth = 0.015 cutSliceNum = int((a-frontPanelRad+frontPanelOffset*2)/cutSliceWidth/2) cutSliceDist = ((a-frontPanelRad+frontPanelOffset*2)-cutSliceNum*cutSliceWidth)/(cutSliceNum-1)
!! Front Panel Curved Cutting curvedCutDepth = 0.01 rad = (curvedCutDepth**2+(a/2+frontPanelOffset)**2)/(2*curvedCutDepth)
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "gs_resol" range [3,)
values "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`, `Простой`, `Откл.` values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0 if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then if gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m else if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` parameters gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D endif
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then hideparameter "gs_resol" if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"
!lock "a", "b", "zzyzx"
hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
